No sensitive information? Really? I can think of two really massive ones right now.

SCPs exist. This guy knows he is never hungry. He knows he never has to eat. Is he really never going to bring that up? Will he really never pass that on? This guy is proof that the world has things in it we know not of.
The Foundation exists. OK so he might not know much, but see my previous. This guy could slowly but surley, via the magic of 7 degrees of seperation, weaken all security measures. Don't beleive me? Once the idea is in place, even as a daft one, more and more people are going to start believing it. The Chaos Insurgency is just one group who could manipulate that. What about the Church of the Broken God? This will make recruitment easier.


Bring him back, give him a desk job if you can, but keep him away from normal people!







